              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387810-lockforconfiguration"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to acquire exclusive access to the deviceâ€™s configuration properties. Otherwise, setting the value of this property raises an exception. When you are done configuring the device, call "
